nnoremap <C-w>gj :<C-U>call window#join('belowright split', v:count) <BAR>normal! 100zh<CR>
nnoremap <C-w>gk :<C-U>call window#join('aboveleft split', v:count) <BAR>normal! 100zh<CR>


